<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>فَصْلٌ [فِي بِنَاءِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«الْمَفْعَلَةِ»</span>]<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>١٠٤. مِنِ اسْمِ مَا كَثُرَ اسْمُ الْأَرْضِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَفْعَلَةٌ»</span> … كَمِثْلِ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَسْبَعَةٍ»</span>، وَالزَّائِدُ اخْتُزِلَا<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>١٠٥. مِنْ ذِي الْمَزِيدِ كَـ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مَفْعَاةٍ»</span>، وَ <span style="color:#6c6c00">«مُفْعِلَةٌ … وَأَفْعَلَتْ»</span> عَنْهُمُ فِي ذَا قَدِ احْتُمِلَا<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>١٠٦. غَيْرُ الثُّلَاثِيِّ مِنْ ذَا الْوَضْعِ مُمْتَنِعٌ … وَرُبَّمَا جَاءَ مِنْهُ نَادِرٌ قُبِلَا<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>* * *<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>